{"tid":460512,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"Intel 將推出集成 AMD Radeon 顯示晶片的第八代 Core i 處理器","createTime":"2017-11-06T16:45:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-08T10:29:13.000Z","uid":1518,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c0a86f793d15a4a8896426795dc68f3cf480ad81","tid":460512,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-06T16:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/d221dd8ee7efbdc993a01b267fa61052/205835821/Intel+new+8th+Gen+processor+-+package+size+compare+%281%29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.aolcdn.com%2Fhss%2Fstorage%2Fmidas%2Fd221dd8ee7efbdc993a01b267fa61052%2F205835821%2FIntel%2Bnew%2B8th%2BGen%2Bprocessor%2B-%2Bpackage%2Bsize%2Bcompare%2B%25281%2529.jpg&h=74d7639d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在讓所有人眼鏡碎一地的一篇新聞稿中，Intel 確認了正在開發集成 AMD Radeon 顯示晶片的新第八代 Core i 處理器，將以輕薄筆電為設定對象。Intel 的說法是過去獨立的 CPU、顯示晶片、顯示用的 HBM2 記憶體在新晶片中將被整合在一起，大幅縮小封裝大小與發熱量，讓輕薄筆電也能有好的顯示效能。<br />\n<br />\n這當中的重磅炸彈當然是 Intel 竟然採用了「半客製化」的 AMD 顯示方案 -- 雖然說 AMD 讓自己的技術盡量出現在愈多機器中就愈賺錢，這點是無可厚非，但 AMD 才剛宣佈了將推出結合 Vega 顯示的新款筆電用 Ryzen 晶片，這下子不就變成和自己競爭了嗎？至於 Intel 一方倒是沒有什麼損失，如果這樣的組合確實能控制好能耗與發熱量的話，Intel 就可以放緩自家集成顯示的研發，而不用一直維持半吊子的狀態了。<br />\n<br />\n這是首度使用 Intel EMIB 技術的產品，這技術混合了多種製程的晶片在相同的封裝內，透過封裝內嵌的高速通道在 CPU、GPU 與 HBM 記憶體之前傳遞資訊。看起來 CPU 與 GPU 的整合是不如集成顯卡緊密，但相對於現有的獨立顯示方案，在體積上要小太多了。或許可以視為位於兩者之間的一種狀態吧。<br />\n<br />\nIntel 預期採用這新晶片組合的筆電產品將在 2018 年第一季面世，並歸於 Intel 第八代 Core 處理器家族之下。到底這有沒有效，一切就看它的跑分結果如何囉。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gaHs_guCp2o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgaHs_guCp2o&d=9m%2BTGA%2FiDL3PBWOY9aJCJviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=c3038ada\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gaHs_guCp2o</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinese.engadget.com/2017/11/06/intel-core-h-8th-gen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinese.engadget.com%2F2017%2F11%2F06%2Fintel-core-h-8th-gen%2F&d=9m%2BTGA%2FiDL3PBWOY9aJCJviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=580eb00d\" target=\"_blank\">https://chinese.engadget.com/2017/11/06/intel-core-h-8th-gen/</a><br />\n<br />\nintel 8th gen cpu+VEGA+1024bit HBM2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e03ff64a3dea2ba47de2ed17c0b0da1d6902d85","tid":460512,"uid":45148,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T02:53:31.000Z","msg":"Intel發現佢最大敵人唔係AMD<br />\n係Nvidia 係高通"},{"pid":"7d0bff0904af286b2892d0da9100c9ccae2c03c6","tid":460512,"uid":53857,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T01:20:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Intel發現佢最大敵人唔係AMD<br />\n係Nvidia 係高通</blockquote><br />\n一向都知，AMD真係死左Intel一定唔好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36e2c9d0f66310d5b57088f02c5f7d1e95fee42e","tid":460512,"uid":79546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T02:31:44.000Z","msg":"食住花生等<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6dab3d4ea8f2023a27b13e5cd845f8fd06a03f3","tid":460512,"uid":34955,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T10:29:13.000Z","msg":"死啦<br />\n班intel fans會唔會精神分裂<br />\n要被逼用咁垃圾嘅amd喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}